This file contains instructions for configuring, building
and testing the code using cmake and ctest. 

cd ~/
git clone git@github.com:E3SM-Project/CMDV-testing.git
cd CMDV-testing
git checkout ikalash/cdash
mkdir build
cd build
cp ../dashboards/camobap.ca.sandia.gov/do-cmake .
./do-cmake
make -j 8
ctest -V

The requirement is to have cmake version 2.8 or higher.  
